            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EThis%20remarkable%20prophecy%20reminds%20us%20of%20the%20foreknowledge%20of%20God%2C%20for%20King%20Josiah%20of%20Judah%20was%20not%20born%20until%20nearly%20three%20hundred%20years%20after%20the%20word%20of%20the%20Lord%20had%20foretold%20it!%20Imagine%20if%20someone%20on%20the%20Mayflower%20had%20announced%20the%20exact%20name%20of%20a%20recently%20elected%20American%20president%20and%20had%20described%20in%20detail%20his%20policies%20and%20actions.%20Such%20a%20scenario%20would%20be%20similar%20to%20what%20happened%20with%20Josiah%2C%20for%20he%20fulfilled%20the%20prophecy%20concerning%20his%20life%20down%20to%20the%20smallest%20detail%20(2%20Kings%2023%3A15-16).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EOur%20lives%20are%20not%20accidental%2C%20but%20are%20carefully%20purposed%20by%20God%20to%20bring%20glory%20to%20His%20name.%20We%20are%20indeed%20children%20of%20destiny.%20The%20Lord%20told%20Jeremiah%2C%20%22I%20knew%20you%20before%20I%20formed%20you%20in%20your%20mother's%20womb.%20Before%20you%20were%20born%20I%20set%20you%20apart%20and%20appointed%20you%20as%20my%20spokesman%20to%20the%20world%22%20(Jeremiah%201%3A5).%20Rest%20today%20in%20the%20foreknowledge%20of%20God%20concerning%20your%20destiny.%20From%20the%20beginning%20of%20time%2C%20God%20has%20had%20His%20eye%20upon%20you!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
            "type": "passage",
            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Kings.12:20-13:34",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E1%20Kings%2012%3A20-13%3A34%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_12_20%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20learned%20of%20Jeroboam%26%23x2019%3Bs%20return%20from%20Egypt%2C%20they%20called%20an%20assembly%20and%20made%20him%20king%20over%20all%20Israel.%20So%20only%20the%20tribe%20of%20Judah%20remained%20loyal%20to%20the%20family%20of%20David.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_12_21%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EShemaiah%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Prophecy%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20Rehoboam%20arrived%20at%20Jerusalem%2C%20he%20mobilized%20the%20men%20of%20Judah%20and%20the%20tribe%20of%20Benjamin%26%23x2014%3B180%2C000%20select%20troops%26%23x2014%3Bto%20fight%20against%20the%20men%20of%20Israel%20and%20to%20restore%20the%20kingdom%20to%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_12_22%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20God%20said%20to%20Shemaiah%2C%20the%20man%20of%20God%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_12_23%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSay%20to%20Rehoboam%20son%20of%20Solomon%2C%20king%20of%20Judah%2C%20and%20to%20all%20the%20people%20of%20Judah%20and%20Benjamin%2C%20and%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20people%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_12_24%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2018%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20Do%20not%20fight%20against%20your%20relatives%2C%20the%20Israelites.%20Go%20back%20home%2C%20for%20what%20has%20happened%20is%20my%20doing!%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%20So%20they%20obeyed%20the%20message%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20went%20home%2C%20as%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20had%20commanded.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_12_25%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EJeroboam%20Makes%20Gold%20Calves%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3EJeroboam%20then%20built%20up%20the%20city%20of%20Shechem%20in%20the%20hill%20country%20of%20Ephraim%2C%20and%20it%20became%20his%20capital.%20Later%20he%20went%20and%20built%20up%20the%20town%20of%20Peniel.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E12%3A25%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EPenuel%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20variant%20spelling%20of%20Peniel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_12_26%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E26%3C%2Fspan%3EJeroboam%20thought%20to%20himself%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BUnless%20I%20am%20careful%2C%20the%20kingdom%20will%20return%20to%20the%20dynasty%20of%20David.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_12_27%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E27%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20these%20people%20go%20to%20Jerusalem%20to%20offer%20sacrifices%20at%20the%20Temple%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20they%20will%20again%20give%20their%20allegiance%20to%20King%20Rehoboam%20of%20Judah.%20They%20will%20kill%20me%20and%20make%20him%20their%20king%20instead.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_12_28%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E28%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20on%20the%20advice%20of%20his%20counselors%2C%20the%20king%20made%20two%20gold%20calves.%20He%20said%20to%20the%20people%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E12%3A28%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eto%20them.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%26%23x201C%3BIt%20is%20too%20much%20trouble%20for%20you%20to%20worship%20in%20Jerusalem.%20Look%2C%20Israel%2C%20these%20are%20the%20gods%20who%20brought%20you%20out%20of%20Egypt!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_12_29%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E29%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20placed%20these%20calf%20idols%20in%20Bethel%20and%20in%20Dan%26%23x2014%3Bat%20either%20end%20of%20his%20kingdom.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_12_30%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2230%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E30%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20this%20became%20a%20great%20sin%2C%20for%20the%20people%20worshiped%20the%20idols%2C%20traveling%20as%20far%20north%20as%20Dan%20to%20worship%20the%20one%20there.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_12_31%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2231%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E31%3C%2Fspan%3EJeroboam%20also%20erected%20buildings%20at%20the%20pagan%20shrines%20and%20ordained%20priests%20from%20the%20common%20people%26%23x2014%3Bthose%20who%20were%20not%20from%20the%20priestly%20tribe%20of%20Levi.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_12_32%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2232%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E32%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20Jeroboam%20instituted%20a%20religious%20festival%20in%20Bethel%2C%20held%20on%20the%20fifteenth%20day%20of%20the%20eighth%20month%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E12%3A32%3C%2Fspan%3E%20This%20day%20of%20the%20ancient%20Hebrew%20lunar%20calendar%20occurred%20in%20late%20October%20or%20early%20November%2C%20exactly%20one%20month%20after%20the%20annual%20Festival%20of%20Shelters%20in%20Judah%20(see%20Lev%2023%3A34).%3C%2Fspan%3E%20in%20imitation%20of%20the%20annual%20Festival%20of%20Shelters%20in%20Judah.%20There%20at%20Bethel%20he%20himself%20offered%20sacrifices%20to%20the%20calves%20he%20had%20made%2C%20and%20he%20appointed%20priests%20for%20the%20pagan%20shrines%20he%20had%20made.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_12_33%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2212%22%20vn%3D%2233%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E33%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20on%20the%20fifteenth%20day%20of%20the%20eighth%20month%2C%20a%20day%20that%20he%20himself%20had%20designated%2C%20Jeroboam%20offered%20sacrifices%20on%20the%20altar%20at%20Bethel.%20He%20instituted%20a%20religious%20festival%20for%20Israel%2C%20and%20he%20went%20up%20to%20the%20altar%20to%20burn%20incense.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_13_1%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E1%20Kings%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EA%20Prophet%20Denounces%20Jeroboam%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EAt%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20command%2C%20a%20man%20of%20God%20from%20Judah%20went%20to%20Bethel%2C%20arriving%20there%20just%20as%20Jeroboam%20was%20approaching%20the%20altar%20to%20burn%20incense.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_13_2%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20at%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20command%2C%20he%20shouted%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3Baltar%2C%20altar!%20This%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20A%20child%20named%20Josiah%20will%20be%20born%20into%20the%20dynasty%20of%20David.%20On%20you%20he%20will%20sacrifice%20the%20priests%20from%20the%20pagan%20shrines%20who%20come%20here%20to%20burn%20incense%2C%20and%20human%20bones%20will%20be%20burned%20on%20you.%26%23x201D%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_13_3%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThat%20same%20day%20the%20man%20of%20God%20gave%20a%20sign%20to%20prove%20his%20message.%20He%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20promised%20to%20give%20this%20sign%3A%20This%20altar%20will%20split%20apart%2C%20and%20its%20ashes%20will%20be%20poured%20out%20on%20the%20ground.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_13_4%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20King%20Jeroboam%20heard%20the%20man%20of%20God%20speaking%20against%20the%20altar%20at%20Bethel%2C%20he%20pointed%20at%20him%20and%20shouted%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BSeize%20that%20man!%26%23x201D%3B%20But%20instantly%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20hand%20became%20paralyzed%20in%20that%20position%2C%20and%20he%20couldn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20pull%20it%20back.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_13_5%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%20a%20wide%20crack%20appeared%20in%20the%20altar%2C%20and%20the%20ashes%20poured%20out%2C%20just%20as%20the%20man%20of%20God%20had%20predicted%20in%20his%20message%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_13_6%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20king%20cried%20out%20to%20the%20man%20of%20God%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BPlease%20ask%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20to%20restore%20my%20hand%20again!%26%23x201D%3B%20So%20the%20man%20of%20God%20prayed%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20and%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20hand%20was%20restored%20and%20he%20could%20move%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_13_7%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20king%20said%20to%20the%20man%20of%20God%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BCome%20to%20the%20palace%20with%20me%20and%20have%20something%20to%20eat%2C%20and%20I%20will%20give%20you%20a%20gift.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_13_8%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20the%20man%20of%20God%20said%20to%20the%20king%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BEven%20if%20you%20gave%20me%20half%20of%20everything%20you%20own%2C%20I%20would%20not%20go%20with%20you.%20I%20would%20not%20eat%20or%20drink%20anything%20in%20this%20place.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_13_9%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2213%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20gave%20me%20this%20command%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BYou%20must%20not%20eat%20or%20drink%20anything%20while%20you%20are%20there%2C%20and%20do%20not%20return%20to%20Judah%20by%20the%20same%20way%20you%20came.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1